(Bill Wilson, <i>Twelve Steps and Twelve Traditions</i>, page 90.)
<li> &quot;Find your part in it.&quot;
</ul>

<p>
So if somebody abused you as a child, it's your fault, no matter
whether you are in A.A. or Scientology.

